      <title>创纪录的债券销售吸引全球债券需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/global-bond-demand-reaches-australia-with-record-breaking-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于央行政策放松、通胀放缓和贸易紧张局势刺激全球掀起新债券发行热潮，投资者对澳大利亚新债券的需求飙升至创纪录水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/global-bond-demand-reaches-australia-with-record-breaking-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 05:39:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
